      • imageChange

        void imageChange(java.net.InetAddress addr,
                 int port,
                 int format,
                 int x,
                 int y,
                 int w,
                 int h,
                 boolean error)
        Image change callback function.
        Parameters:
        addr - address image data received from.
        port - port image data received from.
        format - Format of data (RGB24/YUY etc) See spx.av.Format
        x - X position of changed area within image in pixels.
        y - X position of changed area within image in pixels.
        w - width of changed area within image in pixels.
        h - height of changed area within image in pixels.
        error - true if an error occurred.
